Symbol.Script_3D:
del top addz -otstup_2 if bRotated=0 and SYMB_MIRRORED=1 then mulx -1 if bRotated=1 and SYMB_MIRRORED=0 then mulx -1 if not((AC_Wall_Direction_Type=0) or (AC_Wall_Direction_Type=2)) then roty 180
mulz sgn(otstup) if abs(otstup)-900<EPS then addz abs(otstup) addz max_t/2
model solid HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dns/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dns/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, dns/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -dns/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, -max_t, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dns/2, 0, -max_t, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dns/2, 0, -max_t, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, dns/2, -max_t, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -dns/2, -max_t, unID: unID=unID+1 WALLHOLE 2,1, 0,0,900, A/2, 360, 4000
jt = 13 put 0,0,900+jt put dns/2,360,4000+jt put dns/2-tst,360,4000+jt
addz -dlin_sal-(max_t-dlin_sal)/2
PRISM_ NSP/3, dlin_sal, get(NSP) del top
